Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Garden and Lawn Tools Market

The garden and lawn tools market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of approximately 6.50% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on garden and lawn tools market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth. The growing demand for gardens in the residential constructions is escalating the growth of garden and lawn tools market.

A garden tool belongs to one of many tools made for gardens and gardening. Garden tools comprise of hand tools and power tools. The garden hoe, the pitchfork, hand cultivator, spade, shovel, hand trowel and the spade are categorized under hand tools. In the initial state, the gardening tools were made of wood, flint, metal, tin and bone and with advancement, these products were turned into a range of power tools including cultivators, chainsaws and mini-tractors, lawn aerators, leaf sweepers, leaf blowers, irrigation sprinklers, hedge trimmers and string trimmers.

The increasing demand for smart gardening, continuous technological advancement in the smart devices for gardening to make gardening simpler and ensure on-time maintenance and high adoption of smart gardening devices such as devices used to alert end-users to add nutrients and water to the plants on time because of busy lifestyle are the major factors driving the garden and lawn tools market. The rising demand of landscaping services in emerging economies, the introduction of multipurpose as well as high recital products by manufacturers and growth in awareness among the people regarding environmental protection accelerate the garden and lawn tools market growth. The technological advancement in the gardening equipment by the vendors, the integration of smart apps with the tools and increasing housing activities influences the garden and lawn tools market. Additionally, governments of various countries emphasize on providing subsidies and schemes to consumers who are involved in gardening, increasing agriculture activities and rise in automation in various industries positively affect the garden and lawn tools market. Furthermore, product innovations and product launches extend profitable opportunities to the garden and lawn tools market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, high cost associated with the smart gardening devices is expected to obstruct the garden and lawn tools market growth. The complexities with the advanced technologies are projected to challenge the garden and lawn tools market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

